"{\"uid\": \"newseu.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-19-Jammer-guns-drones-await-Olympic-stage-as-Paris-hopes-sport-is-focus-1vmIz5pGfrq-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ken Browne in Paris  Copied  WATCH: Ken Browne reports on France's tight security for the Olympics  At least 15 million people are set to pass through Paris during the Olympics and securing the city will take the largest rollout of French security forces in history.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 219, \"end\": 224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.0570515463220944e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 263, \"end\": 269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9491082433450465, \"rank\": 0.04394092559742886, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 356, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.0570515463220944e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 437, \"end\": 443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9802535631707903, \"rank\": 0.013617213066516897, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"S\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cecurity will involve 45,000 police and gendarmes, 20,000 soldiers and 15-20,000 private security personnel.\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, around 100,000 active agents will try to keep Paris safe during the world's largest sporting event.\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 644, \"end\": 649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.0570515463220944e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cGuillaume Fard\\u00c3\\u00a9, Security Expert, Sciences Po Paris, said: \\\"There are three main threats.\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a so-called protest threat, there is a threat that is more closely linked to crime, to delinquency.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 901, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then there is the issue of terrorism.\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Imagine a mass terrorist attack, that's the worst-case scenario.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the President of the Republic's bet is that there is no success without some risk, then mitigating that risk with the commitment of 100 percent of our resources.\\\"\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Patrolling near the Eiffel Tower with the Games starting July 26.\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"/Gonzalo Fuentes/Reuters  'Protective bubbles' will be set up around sensitive events, including a heavy police presence on the ground and Permanent Airborne Security Systems in the sky.\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This will have helicopters and drones, while jammer-gun operators will be ready to neutralize malicious drone attacks by cutting their communications.\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cParis 2024 is France's first Olympics in a hundred years and 2,000 police reinforcements are coming from partner countries around the world.\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1602, \"end\": 1608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9491082433450465, \"rank\": 0.04394092559742886, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spain alone is sending almost 200 officers.\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1729, \"end\": 1734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.8769431130418636, \"rank\": 0.0743650878985105, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cThen there are the QR codes that locals have to download just to move around the city and get home, while many streets and bridges have also been closed causing traffic gridlock.\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE  Solar cars and tyre dust: Auto's future at Goodwood Festival of Speed  Mackerel getting Norwegian fishermen out of deep water  The UK village that inspired the Olympic Games  But is it enough?\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 2160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2056, \"end\": 2065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.960639090968998, \"rank\": 0.04006356939541375, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}, {\"begin\": 2099, \"end\": 2101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999997944746821, \"rank\": 2.0520156747213432e-07, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mathilde Foubert, Security Studies Expert, said: \\\"I think most Parisians are concerned about security because it's a very big city.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have history with security and of course it's an interrogation to have because there will be a lot of people in Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2409, \"end\": 2414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.0570515463220944e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A metal curtain descended across central the French capital on Thursday as the police imposed a security perimeter along the banks of the river Seine, shutting the area off to anyone without a pass.\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2463, \"end\": 2469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9802535631707903, \"rank\": 0.013617213066516897, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games start on July 26 with an opening ceremony that will see thousands of athletes and performers paraded along a 6-km stretch of the river.\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Security fences are a common sight in the French capital.\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2807, \"end\": 2813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9802535631707903, \"rank\": 0.013617213066516897, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/Kevin Coombs/Reuters  While President Emmanuel Macron's desire to put the city center stage and produce great sporting memories and images, the security operation is one of the biggest the country has experienced for decades.\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 3049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2862, \"end\": 2877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What do the locals think?\", \"from\": 3051, \"to\": 3076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One Parisian called Olivier said: \\\"I think it's going to be safe - that's my opinion now.\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3167, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I cross my fingers, but I think it's going to be safe.\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's going to be a huge event for Paris and we have been waiting for this for 100 years.\\\"\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3312, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3257, \"end\": 3262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.0570515463220944e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cParis is betting big on a unique Games with a once-in-a-century security deployment aiming to keep the spotlight firmly on the sport.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008c  Subscribe toStoryboard: A weekly newsletterbringing you the best of CGTN every Friday  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR AP